Simple linear regression

model <- lm(Son ~ 1 + Father, data = father_son)
model
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = Son ~ 1 + Father, data = father_son)
## 
## Coefficients:
## (Intercept)       Father  
##      33.893        0.514
newdata <- as_tibble(data.frame(
  Father = c(72, 64, 70)
))
predict(model, newdata)

         residual = Son - pred)
